00:11:00.942 --> 00:11:05.892
willing to buy it, and pay more for
it, than you would if you went to the

00:11:05.892 --> 00:11:10.022
supermarket and bought a mass-produced
chocolate bar from the shelf.

00:11:10.902 --> 00:11:16.152
It’s because you care about the process
of creation, you have a connection

00:11:16.382 --> 00:11:21.162
with the human beings you’ve seen going
through the process of creation, a much

00:11:21.182 --> 00:11:25.562
bigger connection than you have with a
multinational company that makes hundreds

00:11:25.702 --> 00:11:27.422
of millions of chocolate bars every week.

