00:12:09.022 --> 00:12:11.812
to be written based of different prompts.

00:12:12.572 --> 00:12:17.052
You could tell the AI to “write a blog
article about the best sandwich shops

00:12:17.072 --> 00:12:22.832
in London” or the “top 10 activities
for young families in Paris”, and the AI

00:12:22.972 --> 00:12:27.732
would write out a basic article on the
subject that sounded almost like a human.

00:12:28.882 --> 00:12:34.202
The purpose of this was purely to create
content for websites, so that they would

00:12:34.202 --> 00:12:38.922
get more people to them and make more
money, there was pretty much no care

00:12:39.092 --> 00:12:41.082
given to the quality of the content.

00:12:41.882 --> 00:12:46.662
And this is why you might have seen
so much low-quality content if you

00:12:46.872 --> 00:12:50.722
searched Google over the past few
years - all the AI was doing was

00:12:51.042 --> 00:12:56.172
rehashing, reformatting existing
content, it wasn’t creating anything new.

00:12:57.052 --> 00:13:01.578
And this is one of the big
criticisms, or at least limitations

00:13:01.718 --> 00:13:03.738
of the current version of AI.

00:13:04.148 --> 00:13:09.158
It's very capable of analysing
existing information and providing

00:13:09.448 --> 00:13:15.008
summaries, but it isn’t yet capable
of creating anything new or original.

00:13:16.338 --> 00:13:21.668
With the example of the “best sandwich
shops in London” or “top 10 activities for

00:13:21.728 --> 00:13:27.048
young families in Paris”, it has no way
of going to a new sandwich shop, tasting

00:13:27.048 --> 00:13:32.308
their sandwich and reviewing it, or taking
a young family to an attraction in Paris

00:13:32.478 --> 00:13:34.398
and writing its own opinion about it.

00:13:35.398 --> 00:13:40.848
All it does is it takes the information
that currently exists and gives

00:13:40.848 --> 00:13:42.538
it to you in a different format.

00:13:43.478 --> 00:13:46.953
So, at least right now,
there are limitations to what

00:13:47.058 --> 00:13:48.548
Artificial Intelligence can do.

00:13:49.423 --> 00:13:55.008
But it is, to use the cliche,
a game changer, it is going to

00:13:55.008 --> 00:14:00.318
fundamentally change society, and the
world of work, for almost everyone.

00:14:01.548 --> 00:14:06.698
When robots started to replace humans
